_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9RI","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":37930,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/23\/jannah-haram\/","url_meta":{"origin":37926,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Family: Paradise forbidden for those who cut off family ties","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Zayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, this womb is derived from the name of the Most Merciful. Whoever severs its relations, Allah will forbid him from entering Paradise.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 1651 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37928,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/23\/womb-testifies\/","url_meta":{"origin":37926,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Family: The womb testifies on the Day of Judgment","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe womb will be presented on the Day of Resurrection. It will have a staff like a spindle and it will speak with a clear and articulate tongue. It will maintain whoever maintained its relations,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36466,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/31\/womb-pleads-rahman\/","url_meta":{"origin":37926,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Rahim: The womb pleads to the Most Merciful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 31, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the womb has an iron hook attached firmly to the Throne, speaking with a penetrating tongue: O Allah, keep relations with whoever keeps relations with me, and sever relations with whoever severs them with me. Allah Almighty says:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12379,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/20\/umar-relations-good-evil-to-him\/","url_meta":{"origin":37926,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Relations: Believer is good to those who are evil to him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ikramah reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe one who reconciles is not the one who maintains relations with those who are good to him, for that is merely reciprocation. Rather, the one who reconciles is one who maintains relations with those who cut him\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1034,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/09\/18\/spread-fasad-cut-rahim\/","url_meta":{"origin":37926,"posit